latest_release.name: Version 2.2.0
latest_release.body:
- Fix broken tests [[#204](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/204)]
- Require PHP 7.2.24+ [[#202](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/202)]
- Fix tests due to WP version requirements in tested plugins [[#201](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/201)]
- Fix tests / don't force PHP 5.6 platform [[#199](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/199)]
- Regenerate README file [[#198](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/198)]
- Require `wp-cli/wp-cli` v2.12 [[#197](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/197)]
- Allow manually dispatching tests workflow [[#195](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/195)]
- Update architecture to adapt package structure [[#194](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/194)]
- Regenerate README file [[#193](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/193)]
- Regenerate README file [[#192](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/192)]
- Add list of files to report of 'wp doctor check cache-flush' command [[#191](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/191)]
- Add missing behat.yml file and update feature tests [[#190](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/190)]
- Add option to filter check results [[#188](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/188)]
- Update command docs [[#185](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/185)]
- cache-flush check: Return early if a match is found [[#182](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/182)]
- Adapt package structure [[#165](https://github.com/wp-cli/doctor-command/pull/165)]
